OL,4,Cstewards to watch match, banned for
OL,5,Cthree years
OL,7,FTwo football fans, who posed as
OL,8,Fstewards in a "ridiculous" bid to
OL,9,Fwatch a sold out south coast derby
OL,10,Fmatch, have been banned from attending
OL,11,Fmatches for three years.
OL,13,FBrothers Kane and Dale Green wore high-
OL,14,Fvis jackets with the word 'steward' on
OL,15,Fthem and carried radio equipment with
OL,16,Fan earpiece to get into St Mary's
OL,17,FStadium for the match between
OL,18,FSouthampton and Portsmouth in
OL,19,FSeptember.
