OL,3,CTwo football fans who posed as
OL,4,Cstewards to watch match, banned for
OL,5,Cthree years
OL,7,FThe pair managed to get into a
OL,8,Frestricted area, just metres from the
OL,9,Fpitch, less than an hour before kick-
OL,10,Foff, before being spotted by the
OL,11,Fclub's security team and being ejected
OL,12,Ffrom the grounds.
OL,14,FThe Portsmouth fans both pleaded
OL,15,Fguilty at Southampton Magistrates'
OL,16,FCourt to fraud by false representation
OL,17,Fand going on to the playing area of a
OL,18,Ffootball match.
