OL,7,FAs well as the three-year football
OL,8,Fbanning order, they were both fined
OL,9,Fabout #700.
OL,11,FThe force spokesman said: "The court
OL,12,Fheard how Kane Green, 29, of Magdalen
OL,13,FRoad, Portsmouth, told officers that
OL,14,Fhe went to the game with the hope to
OL,15,Fbuy tickets outside, but had the high-
OL,16,Fvis vest, radio and earpiece with him
OL,17,Fjust in case he couldn't get one.
