OL,7,F"He denied being near the pitch and
OL,8,Fsaid he only wanted to get in to watch
OL,9,Fthe game and didn't intend to do
OL,10,Fanything else.
OL,12,F"Dale Green, 31, of Devonshire Avenue,
OL,13,FPortsmouth, made no comment during his
OL,14,Finterview."
OL,16,FAsst Ch Con Tony Rowlinson, gold
OL,17,Fcommander for the policing operation
OL,18,Faround the game, said: "Despite
OL,19,Fknowing tickets were sold out and
OL,20,Fthose without tickets would not be
OL,21,Fgetting in.
