OL,3,CTwo football fans who posed as
OL,4,Cstewards to watch match, banned for
OL,5,Cthree years
OL,7,F"They clearly came with the intention
OL,8,Fto get into the stadium illegally.
OL,10,F"Their actions have seen them face
OL,11,Fvery serious consequences in court
OL,12,Ftoday and for two people who were so
OL,13,Fdesperate to see this one game, they
OL,14,Fwill now not be able to go to any for
OL,15,Fthree years.
OL,17,F"I hope this reassures the real
OL,18,Ffootball fans that we work closely
OL,19,Fwith football clubs and will take
OL,20,Faction against those who threaten to
OL,21,Fdisrupt games."
